%html
  %head
    %meta{:content => "text/html; charset=UTF-8", "http-equiv" => "Content-Type"}/
  %body
    %h1
      You have a new message: #{@subject}
    %p
      You have received a new message:
    %blockquote
      %p
        = raw @message.body
    %p
      Visit **messages** and go to your inbox for more info.
